Win rate is calculated as the ratio of wins to the sum of wins and losses, expressed as a percentage; 
Home matches refer to games played at the team's own stadium or field; 
Average home attendance for 2023 is used as a measure of a team's fan base size.

- A high-profile match can be considered one with an unusually high attendance, signifying its importance or popularity; 
- The attendance threshold of 10,000 is used as a reference to determine high-profile matches, which might vary based on the context; 
- 'Listing the most recent matches first' signifies ordering the results in descending order by the match date.
